messageBody:
We recently moved from 3.2 to 3.6. No one likes the new test browser,
specifically the lack of a tree makes it hard to find the test we want. It
seems you can plug in your own Test Browsers so is there a way to get the
old 3.2 version back, but still use the 3.6 version of JUnit?

-tv
